## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of data up to early 2025, and the rapidly changing nature of crime statistics may not be fully captured. Additionally, the analysis is constrained by the perspectives and biases inherent in the selected sources. Further research could benefit from more localized studies and data to provide a nuanced understanding of regional crime trends.

